description:
VODA follows the villain protagonist, Deadeye, as he puts together a misfit group under the banner name of VODA. This stands for Valley of Death Alliance. They are a group of misunderstood, misguided, and/or vengeful supers looking for their own flavor of vengeance on those that have wronged them.

The first arc shows the creation of the group which is followed by their adventures seeking vengeance.
